Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙  好燙燙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久~等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  請品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉自誇地說讓你們品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我覺得冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧  啊  噗噗塊頭大  給你最大的  給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說你塊頭最大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊  我長得大塊起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃  好吃  芽間！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…給我的是什麼樣的  芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雪集的是葡萄乾放得最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間  我想親口聽你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧  芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  紙紙筆給  用這個傳遞芽間的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢…  哎  寫不出來啊仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢  明明能寫在日記本上的  我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  也不是沒墨水了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再試一次給我再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子  好難受  等…鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在覺得好想睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  覺得渾身無力了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間沒有在生我們的氣  原諒我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道她肯不肯原諒我們不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  因為生氣的話還會給你做蒸麵包嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能因為沒有原諒所以為了責怪而顯靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這事  能寫字的話一開始這麼做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實呢  這樣也就能對話了  馬上就能相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太和芽間腦子也夠不好使的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  嘴上說要我們相信芽間的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是想獨佔她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川  安城  打工錢好好存著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火要做出來  絕對…絕對要讓芽間成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧成那樣當然會累了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:05:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家說要做煙火  為了…讓你成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還醒著嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍著轉~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間  跑的太快當心摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}哎  芽間在跑著嗎  那樣的話我也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}搞什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「無法原諒曾經喜歡仁太的自己」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法放棄呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週的排班能不能和我換換
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排班？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四大橋那邊有個工程  日薪很高我想去那做工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  我跟你說…對面啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}哦  終於跑累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她  芽衣子媽媽和山大叔說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是阿姨她……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叔叔對做煙火不反對是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還生活在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了芽衣子那事後  她的時間就一直停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把她牽回到現實  為此不要再讓她憶起往事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會冒犯到阿姨  但我能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對你女兒…我喜歡芽衣子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了芽衣子  我想做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一直活在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為此我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出那麼糗的事來真嚇著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集還真沒有變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了芽間的話什麼事都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信著的話真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓芽間成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明對芽間那麼執著  通過宿海還能實現對話  為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過宿海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海…  這之後去打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今天會到很晚  想先回家一趟把芽間送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是不想待在家裡  到哪裡都跟著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  想和大家一起努力的說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  她說想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…  還是長髮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  哦不如說這傢伙和我們一樣在成長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成長？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「誰會對這醜女」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多…還湊合…說漂亮不如說可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫還湊合啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太個蠢貨  笨蛋  茄子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}囉嗦  笨蛋！  還湊合有說錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得在看獨角戲似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  並非如此呢  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集壞掉了…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我給你們做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火  煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能讓你們動火藥  但一些簡單的活你們想來幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  這就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很嚇人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這個是要從竹筒裡出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得紅色多點會更可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？  這還真不符合你的形象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  在這裡點火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  那麼這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是個裝飾  為了能夠更加容易地搬運上發射台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  這裡也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}好厲害  好厲害  好厲害  仁太  那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  芽間  很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放手啊  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗  做好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在蹦到你背上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的  芽間  你就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗  噗噗  噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間  明明看不見卻看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  比不上她  無論是以前  還是現在  都比不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  去買點果汁來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了  多虧你逃出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也差點吼出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間在我們的身邊  我已經能夠接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我看不見芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能和她交談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想再見一次芽間  但是  為什麼只有宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是宿海呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對宿海來說也果然是芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那個時候開始就什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經自暴自棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明用「仁太」叫他  又馬上會改口成「宿海」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  你那種好像看透別人一般的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看透的只是你  這大概是同道中人的共鳴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要和你這種性格惡劣的人一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的事  那個  我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們要不要交往一下？」的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的對男性很沒轍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nice  middle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（用來代指不錯的中年男性或女性）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  什麼nice  middle啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什麼啊  我真的被你嚇了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是值得那麼吃驚的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  我燃燒起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  仁太  安鳴的玩偶沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴她回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:15:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  真是的  那麼突然  還真是個隨性的小貓咪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果芽間真在仁太身邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望實現後芽間不就會消失不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到打工的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  芽間你準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和噗噗在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說想留在這裡  行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  當然了  非常歡迎  超級歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鬧得太瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很高興嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興的啊  芽間  果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你看了那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季校服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始還以為只是夏天的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  現在已經穿上冬季校服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間  你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（你好）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厲害  好厲害啊  芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是  家裡的筆記本就寫不了  這是為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多些一點  讓我們再多聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（好啊  聊什麼？）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  你啊  那個時候  那個  我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  對了  我們來玩接龍吧  繪畫接龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  這是什麼  像金楚糕一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（金楚糕：一種沖繩特產糕點）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生背包  紅寶石  玻璃球  馬里奧  小手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小手合小手  好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望遠鏡  芽間隊員  開始搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你所撥打的電話…」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  打不通  去打工了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我的步伐會那麼急促
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間只不過是在秘密基地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  喂  這裡  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我絕對不要芽間消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對絕對不要仁太死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也已經死了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說別人奇怪的人才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
