Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河裡啊  有條很大的鯉魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間呢  想再近點看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  在那裡  就在樹根附近  晃來晃去  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊  仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太  在撒嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠  永遠留在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我  給我留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去把鯉魚抓來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  仁太  會濕透的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  傻瓜仁太  要感冒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來吧  仁太
